def _resolve(expr, ctx):

    s = s.replace("&amp;lt;=", "&lt;=");           s = s.replace("&amp;lt;", "&lt;")

def to_rhino(v):               #  Three.js [x,y,z] → Rhino [x,z,-y]
    return [v[0], -v[2], v[1]]

def box_dims(d, orient="front"):
    if orient in ("left","right"): return [d[2], d[0], d[1]]
    return [d[0], d[2], d[1]]

def axis_idx(a):               # axis char → Rhino index
    if a=='x': return 0
    if a=='y': return 2         #  y → Z

def cumulative_twist(idx, floors, total, start, end):
    n = idx / max((floors-1),1.0)
    if   n&lt;=start: return 0.0
    elif n&gt;=end  : return total
    pr=(n-start)/(end-start)
    return total*pr

            brep=box.ToBrep()                            # promote to Brep

            # side-orientation rotation
            if orient in ("left","right"):

                                  rg.Vector3d.ZAxis,brep.GetBoundingBox(True).Center))

                ctr=brep.GetBoundingBox(True).Center

                if rz: cyl.Transform(rg.Transform.Rotation(-rz, rg.Vector3d.YAxis,ctr))

def build_scene(spell_json, param_values=None):
